        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/071c07f55d3be840c7cc0a20e48298c80bd8ae7282014a99829558bebc6ab1f3.jpg"
                },
                "image_caption": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "黄曲条跳甲幼虫危害萝卜肉质根"
                    }
                ],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "bbox": [
                487,
                114,
                909,
                295
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "生活习性：南方1年发生7～8代，浙江、上海6～7代，华中5～7代，北方3～5代。在华南及福建漳州等地无越冬现象，可终年繁殖。以成虫在田间与沟边的残株落叶、杂草及土缝中越冬。越冬成虫于3月中下旬开始出蛰活动，4月上旬开始产卵，以后每月发生1代。因成虫寿命长，致使世代重叠。春季第一、二代和秋季第五、六代为主害代，秋季重于春季。成虫具趋光、趋黄、趋绿性，耐饥力很强，夜间隐蔽。偏嗜十字花科蔬菜，十字花科蔬菜连作受害重。"
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                20,
                343,
                949,
                530
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "防治方法：①十字花科蔬菜和其他类蔬菜轮作，可减轻危害。②清除菜地残株落叶，铲除杂草，消除其越冬场所和食料基地，以减少虫源。③秋、冬季深翻，消灭越冬成虫。④土壤处理。在播种或定植前后用撒毒土、淋施药液法处理土壤，毒杀土壤中的幼虫和蛹。每亩可用  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "5\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 辛硫磷颗粒剂  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "2\\sim 3"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 千克，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "1\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 联苯·噻虫胺颗粒剂  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "4\\sim 5"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 千克，撒施或穴施；也可用  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "30\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 氯虫·噻虫嗪悬浮剂  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "1500\\sim 2000"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 倍液，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "25\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 噬虫嗪水分散粒剂  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "3000\\sim 5000"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 倍液，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "70\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 吡虫啉可湿性粉剂10000倍液，在苗床进行灌根或喷淋。⑤生长期叶面喷施抓住春夏季的发生始盛期和秋冬季的发生盛期两个重要时期，掌握苗期早治。在成虫开始活动尚未产卵时，重点在苗期，幼苗出土后发现被害，每株菜有成虫  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "2\\sim 3"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 头时立即用药。药剂可选用  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "5\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 氯虫苯甲酰胺悬浮剂1500倍液，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "10\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 溴氰虫酰胺可分散油悬浮剂  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "1500\\sim 2000"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 倍液，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "28\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 杀虫·啶虫脒可湿性粉剂  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "1200\\sim 1500"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 倍液，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "20\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 啶虫·哒螨灵微乳剂  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "2000\\sim 3000"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 倍液，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "22.5\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 氯氟·啶虫脒乳油  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "1500\\sim 2000"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 倍液，或  "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "10\\%"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": " 氯氰菊酯乳油1500倍液。成虫善跳跃，活动性强，应在成虫活动盛期（春秋季在中午前后，夏季在早晨和傍晚）用药。"
                    }
                ]
            },
